Package: cMut
Type: Package
Title: Identify and annotate clustered mutations and link to patterns.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Alex", "Janse", email = "alex.janse@radboudumc.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: cMut is capable to find clusters and link them to mutation patterns. 
             It also provide a stimulation function to determine the reliability 
             of the found pattern results.
